If your play times cause you to solo then build your class for your need.  Nothing worse than building it for the future then you burn yourself out trying to get there.<br>
<br>
I'll say it before Niz does.. &quot;play what you will have fun with&quot;<br>
<br>
Personally I think mega enhancements to our resists will be made in the future..... and can see those beefy pets as very usefull in a lot of situations.<br>
<br>
Pet bonuses as I see them.......  <br>
*good protection for the robe wearer!! <br>
*good for throwing at keep doors to add damage without sacrificing blood and flesh!<br>
*once inside enemy keeps to keep guards busy (heard of a few raids puttering out due to guard respawn)<br>
